channel.description:
lots of pplz ask for this and im gettin annoyed at them postin in tut section so ehre it is
[code]@echo off COLOR 08 title YOURSERVERNAMEHERE Client "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\java.exe" server pause[/code]
